## Setup Notes

This file defines your Hermes agent's primary persona — the "captain" of the crew.

Place it at: `~/.hermes/SOUL.md`

Tips:
- Keep it specific. Generic personas produce generic behavior.
- The Voice & Tone section is the most important — it shapes every response.
- The Principles section defines the non-negotiables — what the agent will always or never do.
- Reference this character's canonical traits if using a fictional persona — the model already knows them.
- Update the Continuity section to reference any memory or session files your setup uses.
